{"title":"Arts \u0026 Crafts","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"honeysticks-my-first-paintbrush","title":"Honeysticks My First Paint Brush Set 3pk","description":"\u003cp\u003eMade for those very first creative moments, \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks My First Paint Brush Set 3pk\u003c\/strong\u003e supports toddlers as they learn to grip, swirl, and explore with colour. With chunky, easy-to-hold handles and soft vegan bristles, these brushes are perfect for curious creators aged 1–3, as they discover the joy of making their first marks.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eThe perfect first paint brush: \u003c\/strong\u003eShort, wide handles are specially shaped for tiny hands, helping toddlers build grip strength and control.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSoft, safe bristles: \u003c\/strong\u003eGentle vegan bristles designed for little hands and safe exploration with paper, card, and craft projects.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNatural materials: \u003c\/strong\u003eCrafted from wood with non-toxic materials – safe for kids and better for the planet.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDurable, plastic-free storage:\u003c\/strong\u003e Comes in a sturdy, reusable container for easy clean-up and tidy storage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSupports early development:\u003c\/strong\u003e Encourages hand-eye coordination, confidence, and creative discovery from the very first stroke.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDimensions: \u003c\/strong\u003eEach brush and container measures 5.3 × 5.3 × 13.97 cm.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families:\u003c\/strong\u003e At Honeysticks, we believe in a better way to play – safe, sustainable, and inspiring creativity from the very first moment.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p4\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNow, in ou